    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete Various Missions and Earn Legendary Rewards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/8eea4cdf735c87291d850da23ddadc52.poster.avif?t=1772076708\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/8eea4cdf735c87291d850da23ddadc52.webm?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/8eea4cdf735c87291d850da23ddadc52.mp4?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The city is overrun with villains, and your team is the one to stop them. Put your heroes to the test in diverse battles: from epic duels to chaotic street brawls, and earn incredible rewards. Collect powerful gear, quirky costumes, and rare weapons to enhance your heroes' effectiveness and style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Your Unique Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/077fc34862ea132a35afa3494da4cb4f.poster.avif?t=1772076708\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/077fc34862ea132a35afa3494da4cb4f.webm?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/077fc34862ea132a35afa3494da4cb4f.mp4?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity with a vast selection of equipment parts and abilities! Mix, match, and build your team of perfect superheroes. Want a robot with a medieval helmet wielding a katana? No problem! In &quot;Spectacular Team: Assemble,&quot; every hero is a unique, unpredictable masterpiece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experiment with Abilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/e7230bfc6099f31bef97cf0072a34ef5.poster.avif?t=1772076708\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/e7230bfc6099f31bef97cf0072a34ef5.webm?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/e7230bfc6099f31bef97cf0072a34ef5.mp4?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Your heroes' power goes far beyond fists and weapons. Equip them with a wide range of super abilities: from telekinesis and laser vision to vampirism and teleportation. Mix and match abilities to create wild combinations that will surprise enemies and make your heroes unstoppable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Develop Your Command Center</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/1ffb1160ea59ddf32f46c7b33494222c.poster.avif?t=1772076708\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/1ffb1160ea59ddf32f46c7b33494222c.webm?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/1ffb1160ea59ddf32f46c7b33494222c.mp4?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Your hero factory isn’t just a base; it’s the key to saving the world! Upgrade your command center to unlock new technologies, expand your team, and refine hero production. Turn your base into an extraordinary hub of superhero excellence and assemble the ultimate team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Assemble Your Dream Team and Save the World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/b31d3d8300e4416e3c2b301aa7acd7ba.poster.avif?t=1772076708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/b31d3d8300e4416e3c2b301aa7acd7ba.webm?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203170/extras/b31d3d8300e4416e3c2b301aa7acd7ba.mp4?t=1772076708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>From modifying heroes to completing missions and upgrading your base, &quot;Spectacular Team: Assemble&quot; delivers action, creativity, and chaos. Dive into the most unexpected physics-based superhero experience—where every battle is a chance to be truly spectacular!</p>",
